OL,3,C'Damning' new evidence could lead to
OL,4,CBirmingham Pub Bombings public inquiry
OL,6,FFresh evidence for the Birmingham Pub
OL,7,FBombings in 1974 could lead to the
OL,8,Fbombings being examined by a public
OL,9,Finquiry.
OL,11,F50 years ago today, two bombs exploded
OL,12,Fin two pubs in Birmingham City Centre,
OL,13,FThe Mulberry Bush and the Tavern in
OL,14,Fthe Town. They killed 21 people and
OL,15,Finjured around 200 others.
OL,17,FNow Justice for the 21, a campaign
OL,18,Fgroup led by family members of the
OL,19,Fvictims of the bombings are hoping
OL,20,Ffresh evidence can reopen the
OL,21,Finvestigation.
