OL,3,C'Damning' new evidence could lead to
OL,4,CBirmingham Pub Bombings public inquiry
OL,6,FThe lawyer for the families believes
OL,7,Fnow is the time for the inquiry, with
OL,8,Fnew evidence and new witnesses.
OL,10,FBarry O'Donnell, of KRW Law, said:
OL,11,F"It's evidence that has never been
OL,12,Ftested before, which to its height is
OL,13,Fabsolutely incredible and damning."
OL,15,FThe lawyer is currently keeping his
OL,16,Fcards close to his chest in order to
OL,17,Fprotect the integrity of the new
OL,18,Fevidence. However he says that it
OL,19,Fcould involve both state and non-state
OL,20,Factors.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
