OL,3,C'Damning' new evidence could lead to
OL,4,CBirmingham Pub Bombings public inquiry
OL,6,FLast month Security Minister Dan
OL,7,FJarvis confirmed to parliament that he
OL,8,Fand the Home Secretary will consider
OL,9,Frequests for a public inquiry as soon
OL,10,Fas possible.
OL,12,FA government spokesperson said: "Our
OL,13,Fdeepest sympathies remain with all
OL,14,Fthose who continue to be affected by
OL,15,Fthe horrific pub bombings in
OL,16,FBirmingham in 1974."
