OL,3,C'Damning' new evidence could lead to
OL,4,CBirmingham Pub Bombings public inquiry
OL,6,FJulie Hambleton lost her sister
OL,7,FMaxine, who was just 18 when she was
OL,8,Fkilled in The Tavern. George Jones
OL,9,Flost his father, Cliff, in The
OL,10,FMulberry Bush.
OL,12,FThey have both been to the government
OL,13,Fto try and access files in the past.
OL,15,FMs Hambleton tells ITV News: "There
OL,16,Fare lots of them, but there is no
OL,17,Faccess to them. With a public inquiry,
OL,18,Fthere would be an opening in order to
OL,19,Fgain access to these documents."
