OL,3,C'Damning' new evidence could lead to
OL,4,CBirmingham Pub Bombings public inquiry
OL,6,FDespite an inquest into the bombings
OL,7,Fin 2019, this was not satisfactory
OL,8,Ffrom George's perspective.
OL,10,FMr Jones said: "The coroner decided
OL,11,Fwhat he would hear, who he would hear
OL,12,Ffrom."
OL,14,FThe lawyer has said that a number of
OL,15,Fnew witnesses have come forward.
OL,17,FThis year a public inquiry was opened
OL,18,Finto the 1998 Omagh bombing and there
OL,19,Fhave also been inquiries for the
OL,20,FHillsborough disaster, the Post Office
OL,21,Fscandal and the infected blood scandal.
