OL,3,C'Damning' new evidence could lead to
OL,4,CBirmingham Pub Bombings public inquiry
OL,6,FIn the Omagh Bombing Inquiry, one
OL,7,Ftopic that's been explored is the
OL,8,Fextent of the state's knowledge of the
OL,9,Fbombings at the time.
OL,11,FThe lawyer is hopeful that everybody
OL,12,Fwill be held to account in an inquiry:
OL,13,F"You're up against some very serious
OL,14,Fopposition..
OL,16,F"If you look at what evidence is being
OL,17,Fpresented and the issues that are
OL,18,Finvolved I would have to say it would
OL,19,Fbe absolutely remiss of any government
OL,20,Fto potentially not have a public
OL,21,Finquiry."
